    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW X5 xDrive35i in Alpine White over a Mocha Dakota leather interior. This vehicle has been a dedicated family car and is in impressive shape for its age. The exterior paint retains a deep, glassy luster, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch near the rear wheel well. The interior is a true sanctuary; the leather is soft and free of tears, with only light softening on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. All electronics, from the intuitive iDrive navigation to the expansive panoramic sunroof and the premium Harman Kardon sound system, operate exactly as they should. Mechanically, this X5 is robust. It features a full service history with recent maintenance including a fresh oil change, new cabin filters, and a brake fluid flush. The turbocharged 3.0L engine runs smoothly, and the 8-speed transmission shifts imperceptibly. The tires have approximately 60% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a well-cared-for example that strikes the perfect balance between luxury performance and everyday utility.",
